{"id":614,"date":"2022-09-30T15:01:23","date_gmt":"2022-09-30T13:01:23","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/kashivakan.ch\/?p=614"},"modified":"2022-10-08T23:28:58","modified_gmt":"2022-10-08T21:28:58","slug":"sku-promo-tour-fribourg-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/kashivakan.ch\/sku-promo-tour-fribourg-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"SKU Promo Tour Fribourg 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>La parole de Sensei Boris pour ce week-end du 1 et 2 octobre 2022,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u00ab\u00a0<strong>Bravo les enfants, bravo mes champions, je suis fier de vous! Un grand OOSSS!<\/strong>\u00ab\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nous \u00e9tions 15 athl\u00e8tes a se d\u00e9placer \u00e0 Fribourg pour ce 3i\u00e8me PromoTour. La comp\u00e9tition fut couronn\u00e9e par 4 m\u00e9dailles d&rsquo;or, 3 d&rsquo;argent, 5 de bronze et par 1 dipl\u00f4me de premi\u00e8re place, 3 de seconde et 4 de troisi\u00e8me place.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alina, Amel, Camelia, Ellie, Emily, Francesko, Jana, Kaan,  Marwa, Johan, Sahin, Shervin, Tansel, Wyatt, Yasmine sont les participants au tournoi. Les honneurs ont \u00e9t\u00e9 pour 6 en kata et pour 14 en kumit\u00e9<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Voici<a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.sportdata.org\/276307ce-5818-4ef6-b574-3458a7f7a583\/\" data-type=\"URL\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> les r\u00e9sultats complets du weekend<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http:\/\/kashivakan.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG-20221005-WA0004-1020x765.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"624\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/kashivakan.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG-20221005-WA0004.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/kashivakan.ch\/img-20221005-wa0004\/\" class=\"wp-image-624\"\/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1020\" height=\"882\" src=\"http:\/\/kashivakan.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/IMG-20221005-WA